1. *Brodu* je oborenom vetru preći preko mora. (The ship sailed across the sea with the fallen wind.)
2. Kapetan je svečano ušao u *brodu*. (The captain entered the ship ceremoniously.)
3. U novom *brodu* su se nalazili brojni bogatstva. (There were numerous riches in the new ship.)
4. U *brodu* su se čuli svi glasovi. (All voices were heard in the ship.)
5. Plovidba posada novog *brodu* je bila prepuna akcije. (The crew of the new ship's voyage was full of action.)